Hello, thanks for the fast response and for the great library. I ran the script and built a version of tensorflow in my machine (Note: it only works with NDK 14b, as explained in the README of TF life).

I included the tensorflow-1.0.aar in my android project, but the problem persists. I still get the error for AGP 3.1.0-alpha08:

Error:Program type already present: R.
